{"tid":630860,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"以戲論戲,覺唔覺得姜皓文係激戰入面既<<太歲>>做得好過<<拆彈專家>>入面個阿SIR?","createTime":"2018-04-16T03:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T04:16:20.000Z","uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b06a412c27be2a3316d080db5a0b19bd1c73153d","tid":630860,"uid":59844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"雖然黑仔果年無份提名,但係果個角色好搶,尤其係同張家輝係拳館對話果短短幾分鐘,簡直係全套戲最令人最深刻既一個位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反觀&lt;&lt;拆彈專家&gt;&gt;入面雖然戲份都幾重,但我真係唔記得佢個角色叫咩名,亦都無乜印象佢講左D咩對白。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;激戰&gt;&gt;片段重溫:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uIkI_UTCwNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuIkI_UTCwNU&d=Ls1nbJgqs3x2s7Xao1cZqb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8973331e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uIkI_UTCwNU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家話係唔係?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675458e749c57b01e228d17a3406a49a38f64856","tid":630860,"uid":27324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"樹大招風做得好D"},{"pid":"f46d9d7b555b9b859aa36c571363c2055fd57447","tid":630860,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"其實佢幾時開始多戲拍?<br />\n激戰?五個小孩的校長？<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得佢做嗰類老粗角色無乜難度<br />\n一定做得好<br />\n所以最緊要係有冇帶引到其他演員更有火花<br />\n如果佢係一套戲有冇存在都無人留意<br />\n佢自己個人獨腳戲做得更好都唔值最佳男配角"},{"pid":"84d0264c8750c2742f2103de8179f24e5581260f","tid":630860,"uid":150014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"擺啦! 仲唔擺? 做得好d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37368f4eb5c1bcb114a1102a79b9e5f0c8266338","tid":630860,"uid":59844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":